    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Bard: States how far they are from the closest ghost. If lying, states
        how far they are from the closest subject


        Jester: Either the Jester
        or another subject is the ghost. If the chosen subject isn''t the ghost,
        then the Jester is lying


        Nun: States two potential subjects the
        ghost could be. Will select multiple ghosts if possible, and will only select
        subjects if lying. If she picks herself, she is a lying subject


        Maid:
        States a character is a ghost. Will always select subjects if lying. If she
        picks herself, she is a lying subject


        Queen: States if they are
        next to at least one ghost. If lying, will only state they are next to ghosts
        if surrounded by subjects'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSize
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_HorizontalAlignment
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 649765280201625091, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Blacksmith: States how far away they are from the closest lying subject.
        If lying, states how far away they are from the closest ghost


        Chef:
        States a character is telling the truth. Will always select lying subjects
        if lying, or honest subjects if telling the truth


        ALL GHOSTS: Disguises
        as a random subject and gives false information


        Wraith: A random
        subject lies'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
